-- H. Ross Perot Family Trust Wins Dismissal of Investor Lawsuit Over Losses
-- Thom Weidlich
-- 2010-08-06T12:48:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/h-ross-perot-family-trust-wins-dismissal-of-investor-lawsuit-over-losses.html

          
          
             A suit accusing billionaire H. Ross
Perot’s family trust of mismanaging a fund so that it went from
$2.5 billion to “less than zero” was dismissed by a federal
judge in Dallas. The judge said the investors can file a new
complaint.  
